      <iconify-icon icon="ph:sparkle-fill" class="text-kidslab-naranja mr-2"></iconify-icon>
      Where Tech Meets Empathy
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white">
      We believe learning should feel human. That’s why every Kidslab course blends creativity, curiosity, and care.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition flex items-start gap-4 text-left">
      <iconify-icon icon="ph:heart-duotone" width="36" height="36" class="text-kidslab-celeste mt-1" />
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Empathy in Action</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">We teach with heart — guiding kids to think ethically and act kindly in a tech-driven world.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition flex items-start gap-4 text-left">
      <iconify-icon icon="ph:flask-duotone" width="36" height="36" class="text-kidslab-celeste mt-1" />
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">STEAM First</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">We mix art, science, and code to create real-world skills that matter — and stick.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition flex items-start gap-4 text-left">
      <iconify-icon icon="ph:question-duotone" width="36" height="36" class="text-kidslab-celeste mt-1" />
      <div>
